{"type":"message","id":"a3bec456","parentId":"f3f26b82","timestamp":"2026-03-22T04:31:31.813Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_66e0ad41-9833-4a1a-8302-05be69a04001","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"d2de82eb\",\"parentId\":\"f0ccd9e9\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-19T20:19:51.005Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"ollama_call_5d1d79a7-632d-453b-b89b-36d86a0e24e0\",\"toolName\":\"exec\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:# **NAVA HEALTHCARE RECRUITMENT: MASTER CONTENT STRATEGY & SOP**\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:Article Type: Long-Form Operational Deep Dives (1,800 – 2,500 words)\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:* **CORRECTION:** If a user asks for a \\\"wellness\\\" article, you must pivot immediately to **\\\"Staff Wellness\\\"** (Burnout prevention, retention strategies), never \\\"Patient Wellness\\\" (medical treatments).\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:* **Implication:** Refer to \\\"recent 2024 data\\\" as historical. Treat the staffing crisis as an evolving, structural \\\"new normal,\\\" not a temporary post-pandemic blip.\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:*You must not default to \\\"International Recruitment\\\" for every article. Use this matrix to select the correct solution based on the specific problem.*\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:| IF The Article Topic Is... | THEN The Nava Solution Is... | THE STRATEGIC ARGUMENT TO MAKE |\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:| **Rural / Hard-to-Fill Roles** | **Proactive Pipeline Building** | \\\"Reactive recruiting ('Post and Pray') fails in talent deserts. You need a partner who builds a pipeline *before* the vacancy opens.\\\" |\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:## **SECTION 3: THE \\\"GENERAL ARTICLE\\\" ARCHITECTURE**\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:*Nava General Articles are NOT 800-word blog posts. They are **1,800+ word Operational Deep Dives**. You must follow this strict architectural skeleton.*\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:**Rule:** Every single article must begin with a summary block immediately following the H1. This respects the busy executive's time.\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:* **Content:**  \\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:You must organize the body of the article into **Three Main H2 Sections**, and each H2 must contain **Three Distinct H3 Sub-sections**.\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:* **H3:** The \\\"\\\\[Coin a Term\\\\]\\\" Fallacy (e.g., The \\\"Post and Pray\\\" Fallacy)  \\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:**(Note: Do NOT generate a \\\"Related Articles\\\" footer. This is handled by the CMS).**\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:* **\\\"The Ripple Effect\\\":** How a bad hire or agency usage negatively impacts the *permanent* staff (burnout, resentment over pay gaps). *Use in every article.*  \\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:* **\\\"Post and Pray\\\":** The failed strategy of posting a job board ad and waiting for results.  \\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:*Scan the content you generate. If these concepts appear, you MUST insert the corresponding link with descriptive anchor text.*\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md:* **Step 6: The Full Draft.** Only after Outline 2 is approved, write the full 1,800+ word article following the **Physics Rules (Section 5\\\\)** and **Linkography (Section 6\\\\)**.\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava_Blog_Research_Notes.md:- Published: 2025-11-23T06:43:24+00:00\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava_Blog_Research_Notes.md:Bilingual Clinicians: Drive Retention & Operations |NavaHC Skip to content Healthcare Professionals Healthcare Facilities Dental Staffing Healthcare Insurers and Payers Hospitals and Medical Facilities Long-Term Care & Assisted Living Non-Profit & Community Health Primary and Urgent Care Clinics Veterinary Staffing Healthcare Staffing Models Guide Workforce Systems Guide About NurseSphere™ by Nava Healthcare Reclaimix™ by Nava Healthcare Positions Blog Healthcare Professionals Healthcare Facilities Dental Staffing Healthcare Insurers and Payers Hospitals and Medical Facilities Long-Term Care & Assisted Living Non-Profit & Community Health Primary and Urgent Care Clinics Veterinary Staffing Healthcare Staffing Models Guide Workforce Systems Guide About NurseSphere™ by Nava Healthcare Reclaimix™ by Nava Healthcare Positions Blog Healthcare Professionals Healthcare Facilities Dental Staffin\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava_Blog_Research_Notes.md:- Published: 2025-07-29T07:20:08+00:00\\n/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/docs/nava-content-system/Nava_Blog_Research_Notes.md:3 Essential Features for Successful Medical Recruitment Skip to content Healthcare Professionals Healthcare Facilities Dental Staffing Healthcare 